Introduction to self-service promotions
PingOne Advanced Identity Cloud lets you run self-service promotions to move static configuration between a sequential pair of
tenant environments, either from the development environment to the staging environment (staging promotion), or from the
staging environment to the production environment (production promotion).
If you promote configuration that accidentally causes instability or errors, Advanced Identity Cloud lets you run a self-service
rollback to restore an upper environment to its previous configuration.
You can run a promotion or a rollback using the following options:
Manage self-service promotions using the API (promotion and rollback)
Manage self-service promotions using the admin console (promotion only)
