intermediary certificates.
Self-signed certificate :
Use OpenSSL to create a self-signing CA certificate and a self-signed certificate.
Combine your signed certificate and CA certificate into a certificate chain and save it in the local file chain.pem. If you
used an SSL certificate provider, add any intermediary certificates into chain.pem too, inserted between your signed
certificate and the CA certificate:
