For example, a certificate for the wildcard domain "*.example.com" could be shared between an Alpha realm using the
subdomain "customers.example.com" and a Bravo realm using the subdomain "employees.example.com".
Similarly, the same certificate could be shared between subdomains "employees-emea.example.com" and "employees-
apac.example.com" within the same Alpha or Bravo realm.
