must correspond to the name of the tenant session cookie.
Once a user has authenticated, you do not need to insert login credentials in the HTTP header in subsequent REST API
calls. Note the absence of X-OpenAM-Username and X-OpenAM-Password headers in the preceding example.
Users must have appropriate privileges to access Advanced Identity Cloud functionality using the REST API.
