FORM_POST. The provider returns the ID token by submitting an HTML form using the HTTP POST method, as
explained in the OAuth 2.0 Form Post Response Mode specification.
When using this response mode, add the /oauth2/client/form_post/ ClientConfigName URI to the Redirect URL ,
where ClientConfigName is the name of the social identity provider client that you are configuring. For example,
